  "excerpt": "<p>The Husband and I each shared our picks for Valentine’s Day last year for both him and for her. We really liked searching through Etsy to find fun and unique gift ideas, so we decided to do it again this year! Here are my picks for Valentine’s Day gift ideas for her, and next week Husband will share picks for him.</p>\n",
  "content": "<p>The Husband and I each shared our picks for Valentine’s Day last year <strong><a href=\"/husbands-etsy-picks-valentines-day-gifts-for-him/\">for both him</a></strong> and <strong><a href=\"/my-etsy-picks-valentines-day-gifts-for-her/\">for her</a></strong>. We really liked searching through Etsy to find fun and unique gift ideas, so we decided to do it again this year! Here are my picks for Valentine’s Day gift ideas for her, and next week Husband will share picks for him.</p>\n<p>I just love all of these gift options! How cute are those elephants?! And how pretty are those rings?! I want everything. Good thing Valentine’s is right around the corner! <strong><em><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/treasury/MTAzNjM3NjF8MjcyODE3OTg0Ng/valentines-gift-ideas-for-her\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">If you’d like to shop the original treasury, you can find it right here.</a></em></strong> Otherwise, click each shop below to take you to the item you fancy. Happy shopping!</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/235722237/gift-for-girlfriend-romantic-gift-for?ref=tre-2728179846-1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Lilybelle Grace</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/218850074/love-art-watercolor-elephant-painting?ref=tre-2728179846-2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Noble Owl</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/221558789/say-i-love-you-his-hers-matching-couple?ref=tre-2728179846-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Bold Loft</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/261723361/sweetheart-popcorn-gourmet-popcorn?ref=tre-2728179846-4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Happy Bake Shop</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/216519568/personalised-papercut-valentines-day?ref=tre-2728179846-5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">EH Design Store</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/255020320/coordinates-ring-latitude-longitude-ring?ref=tre-2728179846-6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Handcraft Mine</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/263206219/valentines-day-card-funny-anniversary?ref=tre-2728179846-7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sioux Alice</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/159620219/valentines-day-garland-rustic-wedding?ref=tre-2728179846-8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">La Mia Casa</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/129951428/you-are-loved-mug-in-white-with-heart?ref=tre-2728179846-9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Lenny Mud</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/221521735/organic-valentines-day-red-velvet?ref=tre-2728179846-10\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Revolving Door</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/257029128/gift-for-her-personalized-womens-jewelry?ref=tre-2728179846-11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Elea Jewelry</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/163179813/love-print-movie-quote-print-gone-with?ref=tre-2728179846-12\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Latte Design</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/158811223/plug-in-love-cursive-light-up-marquee?ref=tre-2728179846-13\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Marquee Market</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/247478433/youre-my-person-keychain-valentines-gift?ref=tre-2728179846-14\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Geek Tags</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/253534321/lavender-valentines-day-spa-gift-set?ref=tre-2728179846-15\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Homemade Simply Mom</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/110437393/blue-chevron-necklace-wood-geometric?ref=tre-2728179846-16\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Like G Jewelry</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Which Valentine’s pick for her was your favorite item?</p>\n",
